<%- include('../partials/header') %>
<section class="about_section layout_padding">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="heading_container text-center">
      <h2>About 9jastay</h2>
      <p class="mt-3">
        Simplifying accommodation booking across Nigeria by connecting travelers
        with trusted apartments, hotels, and short-stay properties.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">

      <div class="col-md-6">

        <p>
          <strong>9jastay</strong> is a Nigerian digital accommodation platform designed to make
          discovering and booking comfortable places to stay simple, secure, and reliable.
          We connect travelers with verified apartments, hotels, and short-let properties
          across major cities and emerging destinations throughout Nigeria.
        </p>

        <p>
          Whether you are traveling for business, relocating to a new city, planning
          a vacation, or looking for temporary accommodation, 9jastay helps you find
          the perfect place that suits your budget and lifestyle. Our platform is built
          to make the entire booking process seamless — from discovering properties
          to confirming reservations in just a few clicks.
        </p>

        <p>
          Through the <strong>9jastay mobile application</strong>, users can explore a wide
          variety of properties, view high-quality photos, compare amenities,
          check availability, read guest feedback, and book accommodation instantly.
          Our goal is to give travelers the confidence to find trusted stays
          anywhere they go.
        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">

        <p>
          In addition to serving travelers, 9jastay also empowers property owners,
          real estate managers, and hospitality businesses to reach a wider audience
          through our <strong>9jastay Vendor Platform</strong>. Property owners can easily
          list their apartments or hotels, manage bookings in real time,
          monitor occupancy, and receive payments securely through the platform.
        </p>

        <p>
          By combining technology with local market understanding, 9jastay creates
          a trusted marketplace where guests can discover quality accommodation
          and property owners can grow their rental businesses efficiently.
          Our platform promotes transparency, convenience, and reliability
          for both sides of the marketplace.
        </p>

        <p>
          Our mission is to transform how accommodation is discovered and booked
          across Nigeria by building a modern platform that supports travelers,
          empowers property owners, and contributes to the growth of the
          country’s hospitality and short-stay rental ecosystem.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

